org.datavec.image.recordreader

Class VideoRecordReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.datavec.api.records.reader.BaseRecordReader
      • org.datavec.image.recordreader.VideoRecordReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, Configurable, RecordReader, SequenceRecordReader

    public class VideoRecordReader
extends BaseRecordReader
implements SequenceRecordReader
    A video is just a moving window of pictures. It should be processed as such. This iterates over a root folder and returns a frame
